    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《痛苦之女》是由“雨不氜天”单人开发的一款Roguelike元素的俯视角动作游戏。<br>主角是被网友称做“痛苦之女”的少女，在噩梦中对抗痛苦化身的怪物获得灵感，梦醒后将网友投稿的痛苦故事绘制成画，画作在网络中逐渐获得反响，少女自身也在一次次轮回中寻找遗失的记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras/c84e58aeb89816768df8751433799b22.avif?t=1759584601\" width=1488 height=8192 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras/93275018a437d8ca039a4ec4dd18db59.avif?t=1759584601\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras_big/93275018a437d8ca039a4ec4dd18db59.avif?t=1759584601 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras/db51ec47a61e1c1437f695c4b1963952.avif?t=1759584601\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras_big/db51ec47a61e1c1437f695c4b1963952.avif?t=1759584601 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras/2b2cf83db64f5fb98ec2b9845585f429.avif?t=1759584601\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras_big/2b2cf83db64f5fb98ec2b9845585f429.avif?t=1759584601 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras/6f3fae9038aa4449ad77a672d4295f28.avif?t=1759584601\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3338240/extras_big/6f3fae9038aa4449ad77a672d4295f28.avif?t=1759584601 width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamst